{"tid":39202,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"(走鬼樂團）玩marching band既人真係賤過地底泥","createTime":"2016-12-14T12:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T06:54:17.000Z","uid":65313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"76f596d004d6853493eff1ee5f7ee1528a3f00f8","tid":39202,"uid":65313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T12:10:20.000Z","msg":"去到邊都要俾人趕 好難得租到個工廠區中間球場練野<br />\n<br />\n但係因為有其他街坊不停投訴而被康文處政治審查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n之後話因為唔乎合球場用途之後拒絕續租（我地之前已經租左成年幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n因為俾人趕呢件事 呢7年黎都唔知換過幾多個地方練野 但每次既結果都係一尻樣 我地又係業餘樂團 唔會有好多經費去租studio練 只可以周圍做過街老鼠 俾人趕得多又要轉位<br />\n<br />\n就算係屋企練野都成日俾人投訴 有一次試過俾隔離屋對90後情侶拍門大鬧 最後拆唔啱要報警處理<br />\n<br />\n（憨尻既係我係朝早11點練 俾人拍門但報警既係佢地）警犬上到黎都話無得搞 呢個唔係佢地既處理範圍內<br />\n<br />\n之後每次見到我塊面都黑撚過包大人 我從此之後唔敢再係屋企練野 連琴都唔敢彈下 驚搞到屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"139471e48ff2884ca605968f2e2aa65cdf3e12f8","tid":39202,"uid":334395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76f596d004d6853493eff1ee5f7ee1528a3f00f8","tid":39202,"uid":65313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T12:10:20.000Z","msg":"去到邊都要俾人趕 好難得租到個工廠區中間球場練野<br />\n<br />\n但係因為有其他街坊不停投訴而被康文處政治審查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n之後話因為唔乎合球場用途之後拒絕續租（我地之前已經租左成年幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 